INSTALL
=======

A brief overview to install the IRwiki templattes over the Sapho templates.  

Installation is pretty striaghtforward:
- Setup and configure a simple webserver with the following components
  - Linux or Windows
  - Apache
  - Git
- Install DokuWiki  (http://dokuwiki.org)
  - upload plugin
  - discussion plugin
- Clone or copy over the template files
- Edit your /var/www/wiki/conf/mime.local.conf to enable additional MIME types
- Rename the IGNORE file to .gitignore

